### Daymet API Test Examples
### Based on Daymet ORNL Single Pixel Extraction API
### Coverage: North America (14.5°N to 52.0°N, -131.0°W to -53.0°W)
### Data: Daily weather/climate data from 1980 onwards

### 1. Basic Weather Data - Michigan (Temperature + Precipitation)
GET http://localhost:8000/weather/daymet?lat=43.1&lon=-85.3&variables=tmax,tmin,prcp&years=2023
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Full Weather Variables - New York City
GET http://localhost:8000/weather/daymet?lat=40.7128&lon=-74.0060&variables=tmax,tmin,prcp,srad,vp,swe,dayl&years=2023
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Multi-Year Data - California (2020-2022)
GET http://localhost:8000/weather/daymet?lat=34.0522&lon=-118.2437&variables=tmax,tmin,prcp&years=2020,2021,2022
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Date Range Query - Chicago (Summer 2023)
GET http://localhost:8000/weather/daymet?lat=41.8781&lon=-87.6298&variables=tmax,tmin,prcp&start_date=2023-06-01&end_date=2023-08-31
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Climate Summary - Toronto (10-year average)
GET http://localhost:8000/weather/daymet/climate-summary?lat=43.6532&lon=-79.3832&start_year=2013&end_year=2022
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Climate Summary - Vancouver (Default 10-year)
GET http://localhost:8000/weather/daymet/climate-summary?lat=49.2827&lon=-123.1207
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. Solar Radiation Data - Phoenix, Arizona
GET http://localhost:8000/weather/daymet?lat=33.4484&lon=-112.0740&variables=srad,tmax,tmin&years=2023
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Snow Data - Denver, Colorado
GET http://localhost:8000/weather/daymet?lat=39.7392&lon=-104.9903&variables=swe,tmax,tmin,prcp&years=2023
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. Validation Test - Outside Coverage (Should Fail)
GET http://localhost:8000/weather/daymet?lat=60.0&lon=-85.3&variables=tmax,tmin&years=2023
Content-Type: application/json

### 10. Validation Test - Outside Coverage Longitude (Should Fail)
GET http://localhost:8000/weather/daymet?lat=43.1&lon=-140.0&variables=tmax,tmin&years=2023
Content-Type: application/json

### 11. API Root - Show All Endpoints
GET http://localhost:8000/
Content-Type: application/json

### 12. API Documentation
GET http://localhost:8000/docs
Content-Type: text/html

###
### DAYMET VARIABLES EXPLAINED:
###
### tmax: Maximum temperature (°C) - Daily maximum air temperature
### tmin: Minimum temperature (°C) - Daily minimum air temperature  
### prcp: Precipitation (mm/day) - Daily total precipitation
### srad: Shortwave radiation (W/m²) - Daily total solar radiation
### vp: Vapor pressure (Pa) - Daily average vapor pressure
### swe: Snow-water equivalent (kg/m²) - Daily snow water equivalent
### dayl: Daylength (seconds) - Duration of daylight
###
### COVERAGE AREA:
### - Latitude: 14.5°N to 52.0°N (Mexico to Northern Canada)
### - Longitude: -131.0°W to -53.0°W (Pacific to Atlantic)
### - Temporal: 1980 to latest complete year
### - Resolution: 1km grid
###
